<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" />
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.5;
      color: #333;
      background-color: #f4f6f8;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 16px;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;
      border: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
    }
    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
      color: white;
      padding: 16px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 24px 20px;
    }
    h2 { margin: 24px 0 12px; font-size: 16px; }
    p { margin: 0 0 16px 0; color: #333; font-size: 14px; }
    .alert-box {
      background: #fef2f2;
      border: 1px solid #fecaca;
      border-radius: 6px;
      padding: 16px;
      margin: 16px 0;
    }
    .alert-box p { color: #991b1b; margin: 0; font-size: 14px; }
    .info-box {
      background: #f3f4f6;
      border: 1px solid #d1d5db;
      border-radius: 6px;
      padding: 16px;
      margin: 16px 0;
    }
    .button-wrapper {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 24px 0 8px;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 20px;
      background: #667eea;
      color: #ffffff !important;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 16px;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #777;
      border-top: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <div style="text-align:center;">
        <div style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;">
          <%= image_tag "faviicons/favicon-512.png",
            width: 48,
            height: 48,
            style: "display:block;margin-right:16px;" %>
          <div style="text-align:left;">
            <div style="font-weight:700;font-size:16px;line-height:1.25;">
              Account Moved to Free Plan
            </div>
            <div style="font-size:13px;opacity:0.9;margin-top:2px;">
              ActiveRabbit Plan Change
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <div class="alert-box">
        <p><strong>Plan changed.</strong> Your ActiveRabbit account <strong><%= @account.name %></strong>
        has been moved from the <strong><%= @previous_plan.titleize %></strong> plan to the <strong>Free</strong> plan
        because your trial expired without a subscription.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="info-box">
        <strong>Your new Free plan limits:</strong>
        <ul style="margin: 8px 0 0 0; padding-left: 20px;">
          <li>Unlimited projects</li>
          <li><strong>1</strong> user</li>
          <li><strong>5,000</strong> errors per month</li>
        <li>Email notifications</li>
        <li><strong>5</strong> days data retention</li>
          <li>No AI error summaries</li>
          <li>No uptime monitors or status pages</li>
          <li>No Slack notifications</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <p>Your existing data is safe — nothing has been deleted. You can upgrade at any time to restore full access.</p>

      <div class="button-wrapper">
        <a href="<%= plan_url(host: ENV.fetch('APP_HOST', 'localhost:3000'), protocol: Rails.env.production? ? 'https' : 'http') %>" class="button">Upgrade Now</a>
      </div>

      <p style="color: #777; font-size: 13px; margin-top: 20px;">
        Questions? Reply to this email and we'll help you out.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      ActiveRabbit – AI-Powered Error Tracking for Rails
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
